      "type": "User",
      "site_admin": false,
      "name": null,
      "patch_url": null
    },
    "body": "fundrawtransaction, send, and walletcreatefundedpsbt accept an input_weights parameter that sets the weight for transaction inputs. SetInputWeight uses map::operator[] which silently creates entries in the coin control selection set for outpoints not in the transaction, causing unintended UTXOs to be spent.\r\n\r\nValidate that each input_weights entry corresponds to an actual input in the transaction before setting the weight.\r\n",
